{"tid":1870182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[同心抗疫]強烈要求政府從香港青少年軍中抽調義工協助抗疫","createTime":"2020-02-08T15:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T15:51:52.000Z","uid":258023,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d877d25b637f7e0261ce6ed02d033cfd4bbf90f5","tid":1870182,"uid":258023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港青少年軍</strong></span>是一個提供紀律訓練，教授<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中式步操</strong></span>的制服團體，讓團員從訓練中培養堅強意志，學習自律自省、團結和刻苦精神。本會訓練課程內容廣泛，包括隊列步操、升旗、領導才能訓練、野外求生、急救及拯溺、體藝發展及<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>社會服務</strong></span>等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFgaRw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFgaRw1.jpg&h=46aa38ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價值觀：<br />\n守正不阿，誠信為先；<br />\n團結互助，遵紀守法；<br />\n律己以嚴，尊重他人；<br />\n勇於承擔，服務人群；<br />\n終身學習，自強不息；<br />\n步出自信，領導未來；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>關心祖國，情繫香港。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPo1dK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPo1dK9.jpg&h=9f9348a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年梁特首同中聯辦大力加持依個新成立嘅制服團體，除咗瘋狂sponsor佢地，仲幫佢地係基督少年軍手中搶咗九龍灣坐舊學校黎做佢地新Headquarter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 什至係開頭由龍蝦帶頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 為嘅都係希望培養一眾廢青可以愛祖国多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋清除果啲仲奉行緊港英餘孽傳統嘅童軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaPckp4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaPckp4.png&h=7580d10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次搵翻童軍出黎只會俾佢地攞哂光環，益咗佢地，前功盡廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強烈建議林鄭特首指定依份義工服務由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港青少年軍</strong></span></span>全包做哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">忠誠勇毅嘅香港警隊</span></strong></span>一齊心擊社會!! 仲有佢地咁多資源，唔似得BB果班窮L, 一定有能力自己提供防疫裝備，減少政府嘅負擔，咁把炮，fit哂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Together Fighting Disease!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a95c1b22994fe3c144e5fc05f22516f6b5b7551","tid":1870182,"uid":258023,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BFxdPjQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBFxdPjQ.jpg&h=c39fa568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由龍蝦加持，對佢地絕對係信心十足啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2035a2acb773fa02243b70263150a570fcca35","tid":1870182,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=675b4206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"}]}